            <div class="adopt d-flex">
                <p>領 養</p>
            </div>
            <div class="find d-flex">
                <p>協 尋</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="third d-flex">
            <p>為您提供最專業的貓咪服務</p>
        </div>

        <section id="service">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <img class="ml-4" src="@Href("~/Images/service1.jpg")">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <p class="mr-4">為孤單在家的貓咪<br>找個專業保姆陪伴</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p class="ml-4">幫忙走失無助的貓<br>咪找到回家的路</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <img class="mr-4" src="@Href("~/Images/service2.jpg")">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <img class="ml-4" src="@Href("~/Images/service3.jpg")">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <p class="mr-4">找到適合您的貓咪<br>讓他有個溫暖的家</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="third d-flex">
            <p>用戶評價</p>
        </div>

        <section id="car">

            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                            <img src="@Href("~/Images/comment1.jpg")" alt="...">
                            <div class="p-wrap d-flex align-items-center">
                                <p>褓姆全家都非常愛毛孩，很用心在照顧也用愛與關懷與寵物互動，是個充滿溫暖和快樂的寄宿家庭，下次有機會還會想讓Pocky過去玩~</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center d-block w-100">
                            <img src="@Href("~/Images/comment2.jpg")" alt="...">
                            <div class="p-wrap d-flex align-items-center">
                                <p>我家貓很膽小，幸好有這樣的服務，才能讓我們短期回南部看長輩。兩次餵食跟貓砂清潔很快速的完成，貓也沒有到非常緊張，很感謝！</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center d-block w-100">
                            <img src="@Href("~/Images/comment3.jpg")" alt="...">
                            <div class="p-wrap d-flex align-items-center">
                                <p>家裡24小時有人，環境很適合我們家毛孩，令人安心。隨時聯繫得到保母，會發照片告知狀況。以後出遠門還會把我們家毛孩送來 Julia 家</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>

